<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>第二大脑 on docomola 的博客</title><link>https://docomola.github.io/myblog/tags/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%91/</link><description>Recent content in 第二大脑 on docomola 的博客</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 09:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://docomola.github.io/myblog/tags/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%91/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>我的第二大脑：Obsidian + Hugo 自动化发布</title><link>https://docomola.github.io/myblog/posts/second-brain/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 09:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://docomola.github.io/myblog/posts/second-brain/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="我的第二大脑obsidian--hugo-自动化发布">我的第二大脑：Obsidian + Hugo 自动化发布&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>搭建了一套从 &lt;strong>Obsidian 笔记&lt;/strong> 到 &lt;strong>Hugo 博客发布&lt;/strong> 的自动化流水线。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="工作流架构">工作流架构&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">graph LR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> A[Obsidian 写作] --&amp;gt; B[Git 提交]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> B --&amp;gt; C[GitHub Actions]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> C --&amp;gt; D[Hugo 构建]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> D --&amp;gt; E[GitHub Pages 部署]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="核心配置">核心配置&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="1-obsidian-git-插件">1. Obsidian Git 插件&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>自动将笔记同步到 GitHub 仓库：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>设置自动提交间隔：每 5 分钟&lt;/li>
&lt;li>配置忽略文件：&lt;code>.obsidian/&lt;/code>、&lt;code>node_modules/&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="2-github-actions-自动部署">2. GitHub Actions 自动部署&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Deploy Hugo&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">on&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">push&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">branches&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">main]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">jobs&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">build&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">runs-on&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">ubuntu-latest&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">steps&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">uses&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">actions/checkout@v3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">uses&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">peaceiris/actions-hugo@v2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="效果">效果&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>现在只需在 Obsidian 里写完笔记，push 到 GitHub，几分钟后博客自动更新 ✨&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>